high_descs: Turn around and walk to the long brown dresser that's along the wall
Pick up the red debit card that is sitting on the dresser in between the two vases.
Take a step over to the right so you are in front of the lamp
anns.task_desc: Examine a debit card under a tall lamp

high_descs: Move to the right side of the wooden dresser that has four drawers
Pick up the red credit card sitting between the two vases on top of the dresser
Carry the credit card and move to the floor lamp to the left of the dresser
anns.task_desc: Hold a credit card while turning on a lamp

high_descs: Turn around to the bench behind along the wall.
Pick up the credit card from in between the bowls on the bench.
Take the credit card and take a few steps to the right to locate the lamp.
Hold the card and turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Turn on a lamp while holding a credit card.
